<paragraph id="E97036DD3F7CFFEBFF26FCE4FB91FC9D" blockId="73.[151,1437,290,1000]" box="[199,1137,866,893]" pageId="73" pageNumber="74">
Habitat. Infralittoral species, on sand and gravel to 
